{"tid":518673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"還返啲臘腸畀我啊！","createTime":"2018-01-03T14:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T02:04:42.000Z","uid":108668,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"43c87f8dce55c08efead4c10f948aa69624abd05","tid":518673,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我個朋友最近返咗支那<br />\n佢今晚喺落馬洲口岸過關嘅時候畀人偷咗個行李箱<br />\n行李箱入面裝住我帶嘅臘腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個賊係咪以為入面有大量現金定有寶<br />\n仆你個臭街成十幾斤臘腸都可以同我偷走<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年屋企嘅蘿蔔糕點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食慣咗廣州皇上皇臘腸真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n還返啲臘腸畀我啊仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6f762a6b5c743d9caf8078143f7ed1823b420d","tid":518673,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"好啦"},{"pid":"324c41d05864d581ac5230f05acda8363d35b3d0","tid":518673,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪真係還呀 唔好呃我呀"},{"pid":"4992980550c8cd4a38961f3d9d2f852b12992622","tid":518673,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，我個朋友最近返咗支那<br />\n佢今晚喺落馬洲口岸過關嘅時候畀人偷咗個行李箱<br />\n行李箱入面裝住<span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫</span>我帶嘅臘腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個賊係咪以為入面有大量現金定有寶<br />\n仆你個臭街成十幾斤臘腸都可以同我偷走<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年屋企嘅蘿蔔糕點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食慣咗廣州皇上皇臘腸真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n還返啲臘腸畀我啊仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8693e9736f4720a1ed28b2f7d69a5b481d0edecf","tid":518673,"uid":127041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"價值幾錢🤨"},{"pid":"f20b50566b194555c9c903b173f33128e3abfa90","tid":518673,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"建議樓主貼街招搵臘腸賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a399f7352bcc7b182a9445a0b49c7fb5be8fa870","tid":518673,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>價值幾錢🤨</blockquote><br />\n未清楚實際帶咗幾多斤 因為佢成日幫我屋企人帶 要等佢收錢先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d10f7d2da254a61fe1e7aa2036bcddae7c17537","tid":518673,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議樓主貼街招搵臘腸賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臘腸賊必須死"},{"pid":"5e6f8cbeaaee7c019c0853c977ed68379a43695a","tid":518673,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚多臘腸食撚死你個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝腎虧"},{"pid":"22ef3cadf46f7a218290b37158aee5f8a56e51b3","tid":518673,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"煲仔飯 蒸臘腸 臘腸炒芥蘭 蘿蔔糕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今年新年少好多樂趣"},{"pid":"b852b4550871937b0a5af0d489200a21abc84079","tid":518673,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"你老味笑撚死"},{"pid":"7e2040e7701385b412b55b13842db1e5c6ea359f","tid":518673,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03